Install Node.js
npm : when you want some utlity to be permenantly keep in your system.
npx : when you want some utility to keep temperly in your system, while the time you are using it.
public/index.html div id = root which shows all contents
src/index.js is the entry point of code
src/App.js is a component for now, coz index.js sends it there
inside <div>{'surya'}</div> you can write js code
import './App.css'; is used for styling
we use jsx which is combination of js ans html
if you write something you need to wrap inside enpty <> </>